PN,30401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774195867
OL,3,CTrump threatens to 'obliterate' Iran's
OL,4,Cpower plants over Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FDonald Trump has given Iran a 48-hour
OL,7,Fdeadline to fully open the Strait of
OL,8,FHormuz, threatening to "obliterate"
OL,9,Fthe country's power plants if it does
OL,10,Fnot comply.
OL,12,FThe Strait of Hormuz is a critical
OL,13,Fshipping route through which around
OL,14,Fone fifth of the world's oil passes
OL,15,Fand has been effectively blocked off
OL,16,Fsince the latest round of conflict
OL,17,Fbegan in the Middle East on 28
OL,18,FFebruary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774195867
OL,3,CTrump threatens to 'obliterate' Iran's
OL,4,Cpower plants over Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FIran says it is only blocking passage
OL,7,Fof its "enemies", although data from
OL,8,FMaritime AI company Windward shows
OL,9,Ftransits have fallen by 94.2% since
OL,10,Fthe war began.
OL,12,FWriting on his Truth Social platform,
OL,13,FTrump said: "If Iran doesn't FULLY
OL,14,FOPEN, WITHOUT THREAT, the Strait of
OL,15,FHormuz, within 48 HOURS from this
OL,16,Fexact point in time, the United States
OL,17,Fof America will hit and obliterate
OL,18,Ftheir various POWER PLANTS, STARTING
OL,19,FWITH THE BIGGEST ONE FIRST! Thank you
OL,20,Ffor your attention to this matter.
OL,21,FPresident DONALD J. TRUMP."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774195867
OL,3,CTrump threatens to 'obliterate' Iran's
OL,4,Cpower plants over Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FAssuming the US follows through with
OL,7,Fits threat, this would give Iran until
OL,8,F11.44pm (UK time) on Monday to fully
OL,9,Fopen the strait.
OL,11,FIran warned early on Sunday that any
OL,12,Fstrike on its energy facilities would
OL,13,Fprompt attacks on US and Israeli
OL,14,Fenergy and infrastructure assets in
OL,15,Fthe region, according to a statement
OL,16,Fciting an Iranian military
OL,17,Fspokesperson carried by state media.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
