PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774195867
OL,3,CTrump threatens to 'obliterate' Iran's
OL,4,Cpower plants over Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FIt comes after Iranian missiles struck
OL,7,Ftwo communities near Israel's main
OL,8,Fnuclear research centre late on
OL,9,FSaturday, leaving several people
OL,10,Finjured.
OL,12,FThe strike marked the first time in
OL,13,Fthe war that Israel's nuclear research
OL,14,Fcentre has been targeted, and saw the
OL,15,Fconflict spinning into a dangerous new
OL,16,Fdirection at the start of its fourth
OL,17,Fweek.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774195867
OL,3,CTrump threatens to 'obliterate' Iran's
OL,4,Cpower plants over Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FIsrael's military said it was not able
OL,7,Fto intercept missiles that hit the
OL,8,Fsouthern cities of Dimona and Arad,
OL,9,Fthe largest near the centre in
OL,10,FIsrael's sparsely populated Negev
OL,11,Fdesert.
OL,13,FIt was the first time Iranian missiles
OL,14,Fpenetrated Israel's air defence
OL,15,Fsystems in the area around the nuclear
OL,16,Fsite.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774195867
OL,3,CTrump threatens to 'obliterate' Iran's
OL,4,Cpower plants over Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,F"If the Israeli regime is unable to
OL,7,Fintercept missiles in the heavily
OL,8,Fprotected Dimona area, it is,
OL,9,Foperationally, a sign of entering a
OL,10,Fnew phase of the battle," Iran's
OL,11,FParliament Speaker Mohammad Bagher
OL,12,FGhalibaf said on X before word of the
OL,13,FArad strike spread.
OL,15,FIsrael is believed to be the only
OL,16,FMiddle East nation with nuclear
OL,17,Fweapons, though its leaders refuse to
OL,18,Fconfirm or deny their existence.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774195867
OL,3,CTrump threatens to 'obliterate' Iran's
OL,4,Cpower plants over Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FThe United Nation's nuclear watchdog
OL,7,Fsaid on X it had not received reports
OL,8,Fof damage to the Israeli center or
OL,9,Fabnormal radiation levels.
OL,11,FThe Iranian strikes in Israel came
OL,12,Fafter Tehran's main nuclear enrichment
OL,13,Fsite at Natanz was hit earlier in the
OL,14,Fday.
OL,16,FAn official Iranian news agency, which
OL,17,Fsaid there was no radiation leakage
OL,18,Fcaused by the strike. Israel denied
OL,19,Fresponsibility, and the Pentagon
OL,20,Fdeclined to comment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774195867
OL,3,CTrump threatens to 'obliterate' Iran's
OL,4,Cpower plants over Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FThe International Atomic Energy Agency
OL,7,Fsaid it was looking into the strike
OL,8,Fand that the bulk of Iran's estimated
OL,9,F970 pounds (440 kilograms) of enriched
OL,10,Furanium is elsewhere, beneath the
OL,11,Frubble at its Isfahan facility.
OL,13,FThe Natanz was also hit in the first
OL,14,Fweek of the war and in the 12-day war
OL,15,Flast June.
OL,17,FRussian Foreign Ministry spokesperson
OL,18,FMaria Zakharova said such strikes
OL,19,Fposed a "real risk of catastrophic
OL,20,Fdisaster throughout the Middle East".
OL,26,@{D@IOU|D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
