PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774195867
OL,3,CTrump threatens to 'obliterate' Iran's
OL,4,Cpower plants over Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FIsrael has warned that the threat
OL,7,Fposed by Iran could extend beyond the
OL,8,FMiddle East, after two missiles fired
OL,9,Ftowards the US-UK military base on
OL,10,FDiego Garcia raised questions about
OL,11,Fthe Islamic Republic's strike
OL,12,Fcapabilities.
OL,14,FIran targeted Diego Garcia in the
OL,15,FChagos Islands before the UK
OL,16,Fgovernment gave the US permission to
OL,17,Fstrike missile sites targeting the
OL,18,FStrait of Hormuz on Friday, but it is
OL,19,Fnot clear exactly when the two
OL,20,Fintermediate-range ballistic missiles
OL,21,Fwere fired.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774195867
OL,3,CTrump threatens to 'obliterate' Iran's
OL,4,Cpower plants over Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FOne of the missiles was shot down by a
OL,7,FUS warship while the other failed in
OL,8,Fflight, the Wall Street Journal
OL,9,Freported.
OL,11,FThe Israeli Defence Forces (IDF) said
OL,12,Fit was the first time Tehran had
OL,13,Flaunched a long-range missile since
OL,14,Fthe start of the war, and showed it is
OL,15,Fnow capable of reaching cities like
OL,16,FLondon, Paris or Berlin.
OL,18,F"We have been saying it: The Iranian
OL,19,Fterrorist regime poses a global
OL,20,Fthreat," the IDF said in a statement.
OL,26,@zD@AOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
