PN,30411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774195867
OL,3,CTrump threatens to 'obliterate' Iran's
OL,4,Cpower plants over Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FThe Israeli military claimed the
OL,7,Fmissiles could reach a distance of
OL,8,Faround 4,000km, posing a danger to
OL,9,Fdozens of countries in Europe, Asia
OL,10,Fand Africa.
OL,12,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper
OL,13,Fcondemned Iran's missile strikes on
OL,14,Fthe joint US-UK base on Saturday while
OL,15,Fstressing that the UK will not be
OL,16,Fdrawn into a wider conflict. She said
OL,17,Fministers support defensive action
OL,18,Fonly and want to see a swift
OL,19,Fresolution to the war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
