PN,30413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774195867
OL,3,CTrump threatens to 'obliterate' Iran's
OL,4,Cpower plants over Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FIran's state broadcaster has said
OL,7,F1,500 people have been killed so far
OL,8,Fin Iran, although the Human Rights
OL,9,FActivists in Iran (HRAI) estimates
OL,10,Fthat around 3,200 people have been
OL,11,Fkilled.
OL,13,FIn Israel, 15 people have been killed
OL,14,Fby Iranian missiles and four others
OL,15,Fhave died in the occupied West Bank.
OL,16,FAt least 13 US military members have
OL,17,Fbeen killed, along with well over a
OL,18,Fdozen civilians in Gulf nations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
